                        "name": "fab",
                        "displayName": "Fabien MARTY",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "hum... maybe a little fast ?\n\nIMHO, this is also a good thing to have a clear error with you make an error with an option name ?\n\nMaybe, a good solution would be to have an option to choose the behaviour ?\n ",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=fab",
                        "name": "fab",
                        "displayName": "Fabien MARTY",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2008-11-24T10:15:32.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2008-11-24T10:15:32.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/26642",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "No, should not be optional. This change is to make Zend_Cache behave consistently with other ZF components, which all silently ignore unrecognized options.\n\nAs noted, this becomes very problematic when using Zend_Config to setup your Zend_Cache objects, as you may have different strategies based on environment. Considering that using Zend_Config with sections and inheritance is promoted as a best practice, Zend_Cache needs to play nice.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2008-11-24T10:33:57.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2008-11-24T10:33:57.000+0000"
                }
            ]
